### Events API Testing

# Server running on localhost:3016

### 1. Get All Events (now shows all events to all users)
GET http://localhost:3016/api/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. Get All Events (Admin view - shows all events)
GET http://localhost:3016/api/events/all
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Get Events with filters (upcoming events)
GET http://localhost:3016/api/events?timeFilter=upcoming&limit=5&page=1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get Events with filters (past events)
GET http://localhost:3016/api/events?timeFilter=past&limit=5&page=1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get Events with filters (live events)
GET http://localhost:3016/api/events?timeFilter=live&limit=5&page=1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Get Events by Community
GET http://localhost:3016/api/events?community=COMMUNITY_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Get Single Event by ID
GET http://localhost:3016/api/events/EVENT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

